{
  "stem": "20978.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They sent out leaflets that all the Jews will have to move into a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They fenced off a large area of a mostly Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If any Gentile lived there, they had to, you know, move out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I happened to-- have to-- where we lived, the ghetto became across the street from us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we had to go across.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wound up in the house where I was born.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We moved, sure.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to leave-- take whatever the-- whatever room we got.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got the room when I was born in, in, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] at that time, they made the best of it with livestock and-- all right, we didn't have any livestock.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But where, where we moved into the ghetto, there was a wholesale wine dealer that had livestock.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was a-- he had a cow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we got a little milk out of it, you know, for the-- for the children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The full area-- I would say about six blocks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A part of Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Said It's almost the-- in the-- in the heart of Debrecen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the spring of 1944, I don't remember exactly-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in the spring.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no particular name.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It said, Debrecen, you know, the ghetto, because they bought in from the small villages, some people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans and the Hungarians, and jointly-- military.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, the-- when the ghetto was closed, when they all-- all the Jews were put-- and the Voice of America warned the Hungarians that the day you close the ghetto, we're going to bomb the city.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they lived up to their promise.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
